videos.description: Kenny Cooper finds a soaring Eli Pepper for the alley-oop jam, showcasing Lipscomb's fast style of play.
videos.headline: Lipscomb pushes tempo for alley-oop

videos.description: After forcing a turnover, Kenny Cooper drives and kicks it out to Garrison Matthew who hits the 3-pointer to go up 37-17.
videos.headline: Matthews' 4th triple puts Lipscomb up 20

videos.description: After a scrap for a loose ball, Brandon Goodwin drives and finds Zach Johnson in the corner for 3.
videos.headline: FGCU hits wild 3

videos.description: The Eagles cut the deficit to 11 points after trailing by 32 when Dinero Mercurius drains a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: FGCU cuts deficit to 11

videos.description: Zach Johnson is spearheading a furious FGCU comeback with his ninth 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Johnson hits 9th triple as Eagles roar back

videos.description: The Bisons are doing all they can to hold off a Florida Gulf Coast comeback, including this crazy bank shot by Michael Buckland.
videos.headline: Buckland's immaculate bank shot pads Lipscomb's lead
